{
  "stem": "5103.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went-- and he started to discuss with the family, how can we do something to hide you-- like me and my mother.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And how can we do something to hide?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Even though he had contacts for these other people, that was like-- he, he didn't have, like, somewhere to go yet himself.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He hadn't made the arrangements yet.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But then, I think, he had spoken about me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And he had spoken to somebody about me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But first of all, we tried to hide in the house itself.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was now in [NON-ENGLISH], on the [NON-ENGLISH] in Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We moved from that holiday place to Amsterdam and set up a little business there again on the [NON-ENGLISH], which was a shop in a, in a little-- that's when all this was going on, where my father gave the accommodation to these people.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But we tried something so stupid when I think of it now, because we tried-- we had a folding bed.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I know just only the other day here in Australia, they've got wardrobes now that they make the bed, where you can put it up against the wall.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my father said, look, you and your mother can-- when there's a raid, you and your mother get into this bed.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And you stand up against it, we make it up, and I'll fold the bed, and I'll find for you, as for me, somewhere to hide.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You don't worry about me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I, I will find something, but I want you to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So we did this maybe 20 times.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
